# Electronic Shop Management System

## Project Description

Electronic Shop Management System is a web-based application developed using Spring Boot and MySQL to manage products, suppliers, customers, inventory, purchases, sales, billing, and reports efficiently.

The system helps shop owners streamline daily operations by maintaining accurate records and improving business management.

## Features

* Product Management
* Supplier Management
* Customer Management
* Inventory Management
* Purchase Management
* Sales Management
* Billing System
* Reports Generation

## Technologies Used

* Java
* Spring Boot
* MySQL
* HTML
* CSS
* Bootstrap
* Gradle

## Modules

### Admin Module

* Manage products, suppliers, and customers
* Monitor inventory stock

### Sales Module

* Process customer sales
* Generate bills and invoices

### Reports Module

* View purchase reports
* View sales reports
* Track inventory status

## Benefits

* Easy product tracking
* Efficient billing process
* Better inventory management
* Improved business reporting

